data.description: This desirable 3-bedroom, 1 half bath and 1 full bath residence nestled in the heart of Alexandria is a commuter's dream with easy access to DC. Plus, enjoy the convenience of walking to nearby shops, restaurants, parks and  public transport. Revel in the fresh feel of marble flooring and carpet throughout, complemented by freshly painted walls . Ample storage space includes walk-in closets. The third bedroom doubles as a den, offering versatility to suit your lifestyle. Don't miss out on this opportunity—all utilities are included in the condo fee. Plenty of parking is available, and pets are welcome. Condo Association provides 1 decal and 1 hangtag for Resident Parking.  No FHA.  Deadline for Offers is Monday, February 19th @ 12PM.   Please remove shoes or wear shoes covers.
